con:testSuite.name: MsgProxy_g1_community_True_2.2true
con:testSuite.con:description: Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g1 message proxy interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=true in gateway.properties, and 2.2=true in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g1 test suite, all spec versions are 2011. Messages to 2011 specs do not respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.

con:testSuite.con:description: Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g1 message proxy interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=false in gateway.properties, and 2.2=true in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g1 test suite, all spec versions are 2011. Messages to 2011 specs do not respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.

con:testSuite.con:description: Testing for Purpose Of/For Use. This suite sends a request message to the g1 message proxy interfaces, with the Community spring proxy, purposeForUseEnabled=false in gateway.properties, and 2.2=false in purposeUse.properties. Because this is a g1 test suite, all spec versions are 2011. Messages to 2011 specs do not respect the Purpose Of/For Use settings, and thus PurposeOfUse should be used.
